  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate ONO-4474 in Patients With Pain Due to Osteoarthritis of the Knee</brief_title>
  <acronym>MOTION</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled, Parallel Group, Multi-centre, Study to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of ONO-4474 in Patients With Pain Due to Osteoarthritis of the Knee</official_title>
