  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this phase 2, randomised, double-blind, placebo controlled, parallel group,
      multicentre study is to investigate the efficacy, safety, tolerability and pharmacokinetics
      of a compound ONO-4474 in patients with moderate to severe pain due to osteoarthritis of the
      knee following 4 weeks of oral administration of ONO-4474.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
